        -:  710:// We provide QDebug stream operators for commonly used Core Foundation
        -:  711:// and Core Graphics types, as well as NSObject. Additional CF/CG types
        -:  712:// may be added by the user, using Q_DECLARE_QDEBUG_OPERATOR_FOR_CF_TYPE.
        -:  713:
        -:  714:#define QT_FOR_EACH_CORE_FOUNDATION_TYPE(F) \
        -:  715:    F(CFArray) \
        -:  716:    F(CFURL) \
        -:  717:    F(CFData) \
        -:  718:    F(CFNumber) \
        -:  719:    F(CFDictionary) \
        -:  720:    F(CFLocale) \
        -:  721:    F(CFDate) \
        -:  722:    F(CFBoolean) \
